Custom AR10 7.62x51 Nato/308 Win.
AWS "Live Free or Die" matched upper/lower with CCMG parts kit. Trigger is crisp and clean with the upper sporting a Seekins Precision red billet aluminum AR10 charging handle. With a Blitzkreig Tactical LR308 BCG dual serration which can be used with most uppers on the market as it has the serrations for a 3 o'clock style forward assist and a pronounced shoulder for the DPMS style forward assist.
DUAL EJECTOR: "Two is one, one is none", a motto to live by. This BCG has a second ejector in the bolt. Building this redundancy allows the BCG to eject and extract efficiently and consistently. This is truly a remarkable and uncommon feature offered in bolt carrier groups.

QPQ stands for Quench Polish Quench. This process is now commonly used in the industry. The Black Nitride is coated by H&M who own the trademark, "Black Nitride". Only the best here.
